DJO Finance LLC: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback





























djo finance llc
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Health Care
Industry: Medical Equipment & Devices
Sub-Industry: Health Care Supplies
DJO Finance LLC manufactures orthopedic devices for rehabilitation, pain management, and physical therapy. The Company offers knee and elbow brace, hygiene covers, arterial flow tubes, splints, post operation shoes, and ultrasound applicators. DJO markets its products to healthcare professionals, athletes, and patients.




